{"tid":51901,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕前走咗去搵ex","createTime":"2016-12-23T15:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T17:22:00.000Z","uid":54050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb697f5a3f50776b5d11090d4eee18b1860596de","tid":51901,"uid":54050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"臨近聖誕節 走咗去搵ex<br />\n以前我好珍惜佢嗰時 佢當我係草<br />\n前嗰陣大家畢業分開咗之後幾個月 佢話好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我嬲佢所以冇理佢<br />\n<br />\n最近我去咗搵返佢 但又怕佢冇變到同以前一樣<br />\n我應唔應該約返佢出嚟睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b43cab5d13264f6f30c4592de3e843f952b7aa","tid":51901,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:30:47.000Z","msg":"約出嚟中出好啦 咪撚復合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090185765b69a27d0389179c2d6db9e00e30008a","tid":51901,"uid":54050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約出嚟中出好啦 咪撚復合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未發展到咁遠"},{"pid":"d251a909f997d7d3eb8db9071be8a1cd4bf4b343","tid":51901,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"不甘寂寞姐你係"},{"pid":"2e4d72292ed456dd9e440dedf01b2c3a0b58070f","tid":51901,"uid":54050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不甘寂寞姐你係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當係搵人陪下自己?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我怕最後大家都唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caef2e5dbdb6d7241a099941b45b583899860a2","tid":51901,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不甘寂寞姐你係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當係搵人陪下自己?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我怕最後大家都唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但你唔係覺得好過on99咁過左聖誕節咩"},{"pid":"356185c4693f3930aea7b3efabde5fac1dc72250","tid":51901,"uid":54050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不甘寂寞姐你係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當係搵人陪下自己?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我怕最後大家都唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但你唔係覺得好過on99咁過左聖誕節咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁應該一定嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過其實未必約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次佢搵我我發左佢脾氣冇理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db1149e5f923a91c136c2ea68deb989c10c24b0","tid":51901,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"何必仲要糾纏不清呢?<br />\n男人老狗，一就一，二就二啦。"},{"pid":"ac73b0c4366dbddbe12b4a5df8dd1c2cd5ea1324","tid":51901,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"下次會更好"}]}